org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM spree_products INNER JOIN spree_variants ON spree_variants.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_variants.product_id = spree_products.id INNER JOIN spree_prices ON spree_prices.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_prices.variant_id = spree_variants.id WHERE spree_products.deleted_at IS NULL AND (spree_products.discontinue_on IS NULL OR spree_products.discontinue_on >= '2022-08-14 05:37:36.671606') AND spree_products.available_on <= '2022-08-14 05:37:36.671596' AND spree_prices.currency = "$1" AND spree_prices.amount IS NOT NULL AND spree_products.id = "$2" LIMIT "$3"
